title: Parksite Settlement Offers Cash, Credit Monitoring to End Class Action Lawsuit Over 2023 Data Breach
description: A Parksite class action settlement offering cash and credit monitoring ends litigation over a data breach that occurred from Dec. 2023 to Jan. 2024.

title: Up to $200K Precision Imaging Centers Class Action Settlement Ends Litigation Over 2022 Data Breach
description: A $200K Precision Imagine Centers settlement offers cash and credit monitoring to individuals who may have been impacted by a Nov. 2022 data breach.
